p if farmcode >= .*Collapse dataset to sums of selected variablessort country yearcollapse (sum) samplefarms farmsrepresented energycropsuaa if energycropsuaa>0, by(country year)*And save as csv for opening in any spreadsheet programoutsheet using output/spreadsheets/csv/farmnumbers.csv, comma replace